    <h1>Lives CAN BE Saved!</h1>
    <p>Last year our family was successful in collecting and delivering more than 11,000 signatures in a petition to the Department of Transportation to make changes. Progress is being made toward stricter laws, but the industry needs better options.</p>
    <p><strong><em>Research must be done to offer the trucking industry affordable technologies that protect our families on the road.</em></strong></p>
